---
const { t, base, isoId } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  class="py-36 px-[20px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-10"
>
  {
    isoId === "inyeccion" && base === "/en" && (
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">Quality Policy</span>
        <p>
          At KZ Group – Injection Molding Division, we operate under a quality management system focused on continuous improvement, customer satisfaction, and operational excellence.
        </p>
        <p>
          {" "}
          ISO 9001:2015 and IATF 16949:2016 certifications underscore our commitment to meeting the highest standards in the automotive industry, promoting efficient, reliable processes focused on creating value for our customers.
        </p>
        <span>See the{" "}
          <a class="font-semibold" href="/Inyeccion.pdf" target="_blank">
            (CURRENT POLICY)
          </a></span>
      </div>
    )
  }

  {
    isoId === "inyeccion" && base === "" && (
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">Política de Calidad</span>
        <p>
          En KZ Group – División Inyección trabajamos bajo un sistema de gestión
          de calidad orientado a la mejora continua, la satisfacción del cliente
          y la excelencia operacional. 
        </p>
        <p>
          La certificación ISO 9001:2015 y la certificación IATF 16949:2016
          respaldan nuestro compromiso con el cumplimiento de los más altos
          estándares de la industria automotriz, promoviendo procesos
          eficientes, confiables y enfocados en la generación de valor para
          nuestros clientes.
        </p>
        <span>Ver{" "}
          <a class="font-semibold" href="/Inyeccion.pdf" target="_blank">
            (POLITICA VIGENTE)
          </a></span>
      </div>
    )
  }

  {
    isoId === "matriceria" && base === "/en" && (
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">Quality Policy</span>
        <p>
          Over the years, KZ Group's Tooling Division has developed a quality
          management system based on excellence and efficiency in every process,
          where customer satisfaction is the main focus from the very beginning
          of project development.
        </p>
      </div>
    )
  }

  {
    isoId === "matriceria" && base === "" && (
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">Política de calidad</span>
        <p>
          KZ Group División Matricería, ha logrado a través de los años un
          sistema de gestión de calidad basado en la excelencia y eficiencia
          cada proceso, donde la satisfacción del cliente es el foco principal
          inclusive desde el inicio de desarrollo de proyectos.
        </p>
      </div>
    )
  }

  {
    isoId != "inyeccion" && (
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">ISO 9001-2015</span>
        <p>{t.texto1}</p>
        <p>{t.texto2}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-oscuro max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">
        <span class="font-semibold">IATF 16949:2016</span>
        <p>{t.texto3}</p>
        <p>{t.texto4}</p>
      </div>
    )
  }

  <div
    class="flex gap-4 w-full justify-center items-center text-oscuro font-bold"
  >
    <a
      href="/IQNET.pdf"
      class="bg-[#EFEFEF] w-full max-w-48 py-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[#1D1D1D50] hover:bg-[#e4e4e4] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
      target="_blank"
    >
      <img src="/pdf.svg" alt="" class="w-8 sm:w-12 h-auto" />
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">IQNET</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/IRAM.pdf"
      class="bg-[#EFEFEF] w-full max-w-48 py-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[#1D1D1D50] hover:bg-[#e4e4e4] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
      target="_blank"
    >
      <img src="/pdf.svg" alt="" class="w-8 sm:w-12 h-auto" />
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">ISO</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="/IATF.pdf"
      class="bg-[#EFEFEF] w-full max-w-48 py-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-[#1D1D1D50] hover:bg-[#e4e4e4] transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
      target="_blank"
    >
      <img src="/pdf.svg" alt="" class="w-8 sm:w-12 h-auto" />
      <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">IATF</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center mt-10 gap-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-36 gap-3 text-sm text-oscuro">
      <a
        href="http://qr.afip.gob.ar/?qr=IMGS0k3IWEcajJvI0inp3g,,"
        target="blank"
        class="w-36"
      >
        <img
          src="/DATAFISCALERIC.webp"
          alt="Data Fiscal BIAGIONI ZELLNER ERIC SEBASTIAN"
        />
      </a>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
        <p class="font-semibold">BIAGIONI ZELLNER ERIC SEBASTIAN</p>
        <p>CUIT: 20-33182478-0</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-36 gap-3 text-sm text-oscuro">
      <a
        href="http://qr.afip.gob.ar/?qr=axE-6P82aAUet3ON_y30Uw,,"
        target="blank"
        class="w-36"
        ><img
          src="/DATAFISCALJOSE.webp"
          alt="Data Fiscal BIAGIONI ARMANDO JOSE"
        />
      </a>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
        <p class="font-semibold">BIAGIONI ARMANDO JOSE</p>
        <p>CUIT: 20-14674266-2</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-36 gap-3 text-sm text-oscuro">
      <a
        href="http://qr.afip.gob.ar/?qr=mA6JtmCCRvsZw2fJJhM30A,,"
        target="blank"
        class="w-36"
        ><img src="/DATAFISCALKZ.webp" alt="Data Fiscal KZ AUTOMOTIVE S.A." />
      </a>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
        <p class="font-semibold">KZ AUTOMOTIVE S.A.</p>
        <p class="mt-auto">CUIT: 30-71889722-6</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
